Ongoti bathi kunezikhungo ezenza umsebenzi oqondene ngqo nokukhulucula utshwala emzimbeni womuntu obesecwilile osefuna ukuqala kabusha empilweni. Lezi zikhungo ezijwayele ukusiza abantu abanenkinga yezidakamizwa, zinanezinhlelo eziqondene ngqo nalabo botshwala phecelezi i-Alcohol Rehabilition. Kodwa kukhona nawe ongazenzela khona ekhaya: * Susa bonke utshwala endlini ukuze ungabuboni * Qala imikhuba emisha, uma ubuphuza kakhulu ngezimpalasonto, thola ezinye izinto ezihlukile ozozenza ngalezi zikhathi ukuze ungaphindeli otshwaleni. Gwema nabangani abajwayele ukukuholela ebhodleleni. * Yidla ngendlela, izithelo akube wumngani wakho. * Uma unenkinga yotshwala noma osondelene naye umbona edinga usizo, ungabathinta abakwaAlcoholics Anonymous(AA) KU-0861 435 722 Bayatholakala naku-wwww.aasouthafrica.org Bakhona nasemgwaqeni uSmith Street eThekwini eDoone House, naku-031 301 4959.